(20, 3, '2009-05-29 19:54:06', 'Magento version 1.3.2 now available', 'This version includes some improvements and issue resolutions for version 1.3.x that are listed on the release notes page. also included is a Beta version of the Compile module.', 'http://www.magentocommerce.com/blog/comments/magento-version-132-now-available/', 0, 0),
